description:
In the Bible, peace is not a passive word. It’s an active word. It doesn’t only mean the absence of something, but the existence of something. That’s what Jesus meant when He said, “Blessed are the peacemakers.” Watch the clip below and find out about the kind of peace that gives lasting happiness and about the One who can give it to you and your family.
